CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 16, 1958, pg. B2, reads: "Swing-testing - Mrs. Mattie Hunt, seated, and Mrs. Pearl Reed may have twofold interests concerning the swinging act at Highland Park playground. Apparently the swing passes the capacity test.  Their ability to operate posed the question. - Photos by Teenie Harris."
TitMainTitle: Mattie Hunt seated on swing, with Pearl Reed standing behind her, in Highland Park for 30th annual outing of James East Liberty Missionary Society of Ebenezer Baptist Church
